# Environment Variables — Travel Ops

Copy this to `.env` and fill in your actual values.
Never commit `.env` to Git.

# ── Supabase ──────────────────────────────────────────────
SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# ── MSG91 (WhatsApp) ──────────────────────────────────────
# Get from https://msg91.com/
MSG91_AUTH_KEY=YOUR_MSG91_AUTH_KEY
MSG91_INTEGRATED_NUMBER=91XXXXXXXXXX

# ── Resend (Email) ────────────────────────────────────────
# Get from https://resend.com/
RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
SEND_DOMAIN=yourdomain.com

# ── Cloudflare Workers ────────────────────────────────────
WHATSAPP_WORKER_URL=https://travel-ops-whatsapp.YOUR_SUBDOMAIN.workers.dev
EMAIL_WORKER_URL=https://travel-ops-email.YOUR_SUBDOMAIN.workers.dev
